Introduction

Lee Dong Yeol, formerly known as Xiao, is a South Korean singer under PA Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group UP10TION.

He made his solo debut with the mini-album Howling on May 8th, 2024.

He is best known for being a contestant on the reality survival show Boys Planet.
